# Carbon Emission Tracking and Optimization

## 📌 Overview

This project focuses on tracking, analyzing, and optimizing carbon emissions using AI techniques. It combines Machine Learning, Deep Learning, and NLP models to provide insights and recommendations through an interactive dashboard.

## 🚀 Features

* Carbon emission prediction using ML/DL models
* NLP-based analysis for environmental data
* Optimization suggestions to reduce emissions
* Interactive dashboard for visualization
* Data-driven insights and reporting

## 🧠 Technologies Used

* Python
* Machine Learning (Scikit-learn)
* Deep Learning (TensorFlow / PyTorch)
* NLP techniques
* Dashboard (Streamlit / Flask / Power BI)

## 📊 Modules

* Data Collection & Preprocessing
* Emission Prediction Model
* NLP Analysis Module
* Optimization Engine
* Dashboard Visualization

## ▶️ How to Run

1. Install dependencies
2. Run main file / dashboard
3. Upload dataset (if required)

## 📁 Project Structure

* src/ → core code
* models/ → trained models
* data/ → datasets
* dashboard/ → UI
* docs/ → report & PPT

